drop table "CON_Meas" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_Meas" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_Meas"
(
"MeasID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"SAPContractCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"ObjectType" VARCHAR2(10) default 'IL' not null,
"ObjectID" VARCHAR2(100) default '0010' not null,
"Measurement" VARCHAR2(20) default 'Y001',
"MeasStartDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
"MeasEndDate" TIMESTAMP not null,
"MeasAmount" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"MeterUnit" VARCHAR(10) default 'CNY' not null,
"ISOUnit" VARCHAR(10) default 'CNY' not null,
"ChangeIndicator" CHAR(1) default 'N' not null,
"SyncSAPflag" INTEGER default 0 not null,
constraint PK_CON_MEAS primary key ("MeasID")
);

comment on column "CON_Meas"."ObjectType" is
'对应SAP的CONTRACT_OBJECT_TYPE
如启用浮动定价，默认输入 "IL"';

comment on column "CON_Meas"."ObjectID" is
'对应SAP的CONTRACT_OBJECT_ID
如启用浮动定价，默认输入 "0010"';

comment on column "CON_Meas"."Measurement" is
'对应SAP的MEASUREMENT
如启用浮动定价，默认输入Y001';

comment on column "CON_Meas"."MeasStartDate" is
'对应SAP的VALID_FROM';

comment on column "CON_Meas"."MeasEndDate" is
'对应SAP的VALID_TO';

comment on column "CON_Meas"."MeasAmount" is
'对应SAP的VALUE_AVAIL';

comment on column "CON_Meas"."MeterUnit" is
'对应SAP的UNIT';

comment on column "CON_Meas"."ISOUnit" is
'对应SAP的UNIT_ISO';

comment on column "CON_Meas"."ChangeIndicator" is
'N:初始创建
I:新增
D:删除';
